Export keyring Entries

Source: R/authentication.R
keyring_export.Rd

keyring_export creates JSON output for available keyrings

Usage

keyring_export(keyring = NULL, as.raw = FALSE)

Arguments

keyring

(string[]) The name(s) of keyrings to export (defaults to all named keyrings when calling keyring_list)

as.raw

(logical | FALSE) Should each entry be cast as a raw vector?

Value

Keyring entries as JSON or raw-encoded JSON

See also

Other Authentication Functions: gen_pass(), keyring_import(), kr_key()
